Author: SpaceWhale88
Text: If you have to ask if you truly have an eating disorder you do. Do you obsess about food? Do you restrict? Overeat? Eat at maintenance? Feel guilty about eating? Stress over how many calories you are or aren't eating? Are you underweight, overweight, or normal weight? Do you often wonder if you are sick enough for help? Then guess what! You have an eating disorder!   Very few of us here think we are sick enough. ONE OF US! ONE OF US!
